<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Confirm Your Login</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #4a90e2;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: block;
      width: 220px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #357ab8;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 4px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Confirm Your Login</h1>
    <p>Hey there,</p>
    <p>
      We noticed you recently tried to log in to your account. To make sure it’s really you,
      please click the button below to confirm your login.
    </p>
    <a href="{{confirmationLink}}" class="button">Yes, It's Me!</a>
    <p>
      If you didn't request this, don't worry—you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thanks for being part of our community!</p>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Resend Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
